UBS therefore more or less admitted to having been accessory to tax evasion.
However, UBS lost something that has always been its advantage when competing for rich clients - the fog of secretion.
Swiss banking secret was not the same after the scandal.
The CEO and Chairman then resigned and the CEO and Chairman took their position.
The exodus of client money started.
